\end_inset

.
 Hence, we considered a worst-case scenario in which individuals will not
 have access to healthcare and assumed that all critical cases (those requiring
 ICU care) would die.
 We simulated two possible scenarios for the fate of severe cases (those
 requiring hospitalization but not ICU care): one in which all cases recover,
 and another in which all die.
